  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936650/extras/8643f94abd0240a92d43193715e9cbae.poster.avif?t=1749384155\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936650/extras/8643f94abd0240a92d43193715e9cbae.webm?t=1749384155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936650/extras/8643f94abd0240a92d43193715e9cbae.mp4?t=1749384155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take on the role of managing a group of wizards who have arrived in a new world. Start by managing one planet. Build buildings, assign people to industries. Build more buildings. Capture nearby planets and expand your influence.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 100 planets (randomly generated) <br></li><li>80 types of research (20 for each element)<br></li><li>More than 40 different buildings<br></li><li>A limited field of 15x11 cells to build on each planet<br></li><li>6 types of military units (spirits)<br></li><li>More than 30 types of resources (including people)</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936650/extras/96becbe13f5873327da02e4cf51c4fed.poster.avif?t=1749384155\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936650/extras/96becbe13f5873327da02e4cf51c4fed.webm?t=1749384155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2936650/extras/96becbe13f5873327da02e4cf51c4fed.mp4?t=1749384155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
